🔧 Complete Command List — Defect Detection System
Step 0: Navigate to Project Directory
powershell
cd C:\Users\RohithSuryaCKM\Downloads\Projects\Image_detection
Step 1: Activate Virtual Environment
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\activate
Step 2: Install Dependencies (one-time setup)
powershell
pip install -r requirements.txt
Step 3: Validate Images
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\validate_images.py --images dataset\images\train
Step 4: Augment Dataset (if you have a small dataset)
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\augment_dataset.py --images dataset\images\train --labels dataset\labels\train --multiplier 5 --level medium
Step 5: Train the Model
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\train_model.py --data config\dataset.yaml --epochs 100 --batch 16 --imgsz 640 --patience 20 --device 0 --weights yolo11m.pt
Step 6: Evaluate the Model
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\evaluate_model.py --model <path_to_best.pt> --data config\dataset.yaml --device 0 --split test
Replace <path_to_best.pt> with the actual path printed after training, e.g. models\defect_yolo11m_20260305_...\weights\best.pt

Step 7: Compare Training Runs
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\compare_runs.py
Step 8: Export Model for Production
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\export_model.py <path_to_best.pt> --format onnx --imgsz 640
Step 9: Run Production Inference (Defect Detection)
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\defect_detector.py --model <path_to_best.pt> --config config\system_config.json
Step 10: Webcam Demo (optional, for quick testing)
powershell
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\webcam_demo.py
🚀 One-Command Pipeline (runs everything automatically)
Instead of running steps 3–8 individually, you can use the master pipeline script:

powershell
# Full pipeline (Validate → Augment → Train → Evaluate → Compare)
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\run_pipeline.py --mode full --preset small_dataset
# Train + Evaluate only (skip augmentation)
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\run_pipeline.py --mode train-eval --preset small_dataset
# Quick test run (20 epochs)
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\run_pipeline.py --mode full --preset fast_training
# Evaluate an existing model only
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\run_pipeline.py --mode eval-only --model models\best.pt
# Augment dataset only
.\defect_env_gpu311\Scripts\python.exe scripts\run_pipeline.py --mode augment-only --multiplier 10 --aug-level heavy
